put/src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/kitchen/domain/KitchenOrder.java)\n   - Removed: `extends PanacheEntity`\n   - Removed: `import io.quarkus.hibernate.orm.panache.PanacheEntity`\n   - Removed: `schema = \"kitchen\"` from @Table annotation\n   - Added: `@Id @GeneratedValue(strategy = GenerationType.IDENTITY) private Long id;`\n   - Added: `getId()` and `setId()` methods\n\n#### Repository Classes (3 files)\n\n5. **BaristaRepository.java** (/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/barista/domain/BaristaRepository.java)\n   - Completely rewritten to use EntityManager instead of PanacheRepository\n   - Uses `@PersistenceContext(unitName = \"coffeeshop\")`\n\n6. **KitchenOrderRepository.java** (/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/kitchen/domain/KitchenOrderRepository.java)\n   - Completely rewritten to use EntityManager instead of PanacheRepository\n   - Uses `@PersistenceContext(unitName = \"coffeeshop\")`\n\n7. **OrderRepository.java** (/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/infrastructure/OrderRepository.java)\n   - Completely rewritten to use EntityManager instead of PanacheRepository\n   - Uses `@PersistenceContext(unitName = \"coffeeshop\")`\n   - Added methods: `persist()`, `persistAndFlush()`, `findById()`\n\n#### Service Interfaces (3 files)\n\n8. **OrderService.java** (/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__coffee-shop__quarkus__jakarta/run_3/output/src/main/java/io/quarkuscoffeeshop/coffeeshop/counter/api/OrderService.java)\n   - Changed: `onOrderUp(final Message message)` to `onOrderUp(fi