{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01Hd5jDpDSByzHmcAE4dLwzb","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Migration Summary\n\n### Frameworks: `Quarkus 3.30.5` -> `Jakarta EE 10` (Open Liberty)\n\n**Overall Outcome: SUCCESS** - The application builds, runs, and passes all tests.\n\n### File Tree\n\n```\nModified:\n- pom.xml: Replaced all Quarkus deps with Jakarta EE 10 API + Jackson + H2, changed packaging to WAR\n- Dockerfile: Multi-stage build with maven builder + Open Liberty full runtime\n- src/main/resources/application.properties: Stripped Quarkus-specific config\n- src/main/java/.../domain/Order.java: Removed PanacheEntityBase, standard JPA\n- src/main/java/.../domain/LineItem.java: Removed PanacheEntityBase, standard JPA\n- src/main/java/.../barista/domain/BaristaItem.java: Removed PanacheEntity, added @Id\n- src/main/java/.../kitchen/domain/KitchenOrder.java: Removed PanacheEntity, added @Id\n- src/main/java/.../barista/domain/BaristaRepository.java: EntityManager-based\n- src/main/java/.../kitchen/domain/KitchenOrderRepository.java: EntityManager-based\n- src/main/java/.../infrastructure/OrderRepository.java: EntityManager-based\n- src/main/java/.../counter/api/OrderService.java: String params instead of Message\n- src/main/java/.../counter/OrderServiceImpl.java: CdiEventBus instead of Vert.x\n- src/main/java/.../barista/api/Barista.java: String params\n- src/main/java/.../barista/BaristaImpl.java: Inactive reference impl\n- src/main/java/.../barista/BaristaOutpostImpl.java: CdiEventBus, no Kafka\n- src/main/java/.../kitchen/Kitchen.java: String params\n- src/main/java/.../kitchen/KitchenImpl.java: CdiEventBus\n- src/main/java/.../web/CoffeeshopApiResource.java: Pure JAX-RS\n- src/main/java/.../web/WebResource.java: Manual template loading\n- src/main/java/.../web/DashboardEndpoint.java: JAX-RS SSE\n- src/test/java/.../web/CoffeeshopApiResourceTest.java: Unit test\n- src/test/java/.../web/CoffeeshopApiResourceIT.java: Unit test\n- src/test/java/.../counter/OrderServiceTest.java: Unit test\n- src/test/java/.../counter/OrderServiceOrderUpTest.java: Unit test\n- src/test/java/.../barista/BaristaTest.java: Unit test\n- src/test/java/.../kitchen/KitchenTest.java: Unit test\n\nAdded:\n- src/main/liberty/config/server.xml: Open Liberty server config (Jakarta EE 10, H2 datasource)\n- src/main/resources/META-INF/persistence.xml: JPA persistence config (EclipseLink)\n- src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/beans.xml: CDI bean discovery config\n- src/main/java/.../infrastructure/CdiEventBus.java: In-memory event bus replacing Vert.x\n- src/main/java/.../web/JakartaApplication.java: JAX-RS Application class\n- src/main/java/.../web/JacksonConfig.java: Jackson ObjectMapper provider\n- src/main/resources/META-INF/resources/coffeeshopTemplate.html: Template for WebResource\n- smoke-tests.sh: 6 HTTP smoke tests for container validation\n- CHANGELOG.md: Full migration log\n```\n\n### Test Results\n- **Unit Tests:** 13/13 passing\n- **Smoke Tests:** 6/6 passing (Homepage, 3x Place Order, Dashboard SSE, Message endpoint)\n\n### Key Architectural Changes\n1. **Panache -> JPA EntityManager**: Standard Jakarta Persistence with EclipseLink\n2. **Vert.x EventBus -> CdiEventBus**: Custom CDI `@ApplicationScoped` event bus with topic-based pub/sub\n3. **Kafka -> In-process**: Barista/Kitchen services consume events via CdiEventBus\n4. **Qute -> Manual template**: HTML loaded from classpath with string replacement\n5. **Quarkus dev mode -> Open Liberty**: Full Jakarta EE 10 runtime on OpenJ9"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":117,"cache_read_input_tokens":134818,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":117,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":1089},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"887ed637-45f4-4598-acb3-9e086d9e5f12","uuid":"eb5a1f2c-c326-4f37-850d-462fd7c2f333"}
